Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.47,0:00:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我名为伊泽尔坎特
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.37,0:00:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维甘在此宣布
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.17,0:00:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正式开始侵略地球
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.48,0:00:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温蒂 孩子们拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.36,0:00:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉欧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.56,0:00:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有事要做
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.43,0:00:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉欧 上来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.67,0:00:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.51,0:00:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道我们去哪儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.50,0:00:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去启动高达
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.69,0:00:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 救世主登场了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.54,0:00:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.41,0:00:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是…高达
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.79,0:00:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.30,0:00:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又与我作对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.52,0:00:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉欧 小心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.95,0:00:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他从上面来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.54,0:01:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火星移民计划
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.20,0:01:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因其失败被遗留在火星圈的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.37,0:01:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自称独立国家维甘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.04,0:01:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向地球联邦政府宣战
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.92,0:01:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争开始 已近70年
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTA------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.34,0:03:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.60,0:03:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它和其他机动战士完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.62,0:03:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 别大意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.75,0:03:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.36,0:03:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶舱里的是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.68,0:03:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特·明日野吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.96,0:03:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但另一个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.77,0:03:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉欧 天神号能改变战况
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.99,0:03:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在想办法坚持
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.38,0:04:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德比克
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.43,0:04:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德比克
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.16,0:04:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球是我们的星球
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.11,0:04:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会放弃的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.86,0:04:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德比克
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥迪克 振作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.87,0:05:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这群该死的恐龙！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.89,0:05:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥利巴诺兹仍在交战状态
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.36,0:05:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各城市损失加剧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.77,0:05:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与总司令部恢复联系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.32,0:05:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播放影像
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.84,0:05:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好您在这里 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.28,0:05:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾伦格雷亚斯提督 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.04,0:05:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.64,0:05:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说这种情况？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.21,0:05:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 从现在起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.85,0:05:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失落·楼兰就是联邦军的新指挥部
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.24,0:05:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须粉碎维甘及伊泽尔坎特的野心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.26,0:05:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾伦格雷亚斯提督 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.82,0:05:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.79,0:05:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥利巴诺兹 3号线
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.65,0:06:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督 我想应该让您知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.80,0:06:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方才 前总司令菲利特·明日野来电
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.20,0:06:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前总司令来电？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.74,0:06:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 要求出动动态保养中的天神号
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.27,0:06:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是那位大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.50,0:06:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在也无权指挥军队
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.41,0:06:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下打算拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.51,0:06:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即出动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.92,0:06:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.97,0:06:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出动天神号！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.65,0:06:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日野老司令有他的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.41,0:06:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.87,0:06:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.45,0:06:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥迪克的驾驶舱盖被卡住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.18,0:06:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快安排营救
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.48,0:06:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.78,0:06:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然无视前线的判断
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.32,0:06:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却优先退役军官的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.88,0:06:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种老旧战舰 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.29,0:07:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出动也不会有所作为
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.38,0:07:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说 火烧眉毛的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.60,0:07:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我哪里去找一船乘员？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.23,0:07:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩一些问题兵源
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.37,0:07:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给那艘船正好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.36,0:07:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机师呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.02,0:07:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼下只有阿比斯队…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.75,0:07:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就它了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.13,0:07:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正是总司令部的主意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就差舰长了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.01,0:07:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试试有意思的人选吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.21,0:07:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.64,0:07:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还会是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.34,0:07:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠老爸升迁的官二代
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.23,0:07:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.19,0:07:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.67,0:07:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会马上好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.79,0:07:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 温蒂姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.23,0:07:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.57,0:07:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳图尔小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.67,0:07:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 妈妈她们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.93,0:07:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在帮忙找避难所
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.37,0:07:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会有事的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.23,0:08:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.11,0:08:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.25,0:08:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对的 绝对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.91,0:08:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闲着也是闲着 我们玩这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.06,0:08:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 我想去看机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.74,0:08:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.14,0:08:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我比较喜欢这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.05,0:08:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳图尔·艾娜斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.83,0:08:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令找你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.37,0:08:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.94,0:08:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.76,0:08:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.17,0:08:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我去当天神号舰长？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.62,0:08:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 你能胜任
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.99,0:08:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.03,0:08:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不够格当舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.73,0:08:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火线任命你从今天起晋升少校
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.24,0:08:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.42,0:08:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有参加舰船指挥的研修课吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然没有实践经验…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.99,0:08:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我一直在做基地内勤…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.68,0:08:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你告诉我！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.47,0:08:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是情况危机
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.92,0:08:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们需要你这样的年轻人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.94,0:09:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是艾娜斯中将的孙女吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.20,0:09:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有做不到的道理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.11,0:09:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.42,0:09:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.65,0:09:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这艘天神号
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.15,0:09:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定很配明日野老司令的胃口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.48,0:09:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.78,0:09:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要振作！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.39,0:10:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.88,0:10:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.49,0:10:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊… 在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.52,0:10:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是天神号的舰长吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.46,0:10:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.98,0:10:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下纳图尔·艾娜斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.80,0:10:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是机动战士队队长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.65,0:10:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舍利奇·阿比斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.24,0:10:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出击命令已经下达
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.09,0:10:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.07,0:10:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.73,0:10:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚被提拔为舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.06,0:10:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有自信是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.14,0:10:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.49,0:10:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帽子戴歪了 说明穿不惯舰长服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.29,0:10:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帽子系得太紧 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.12,0:10:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想隐瞒自信心的缺乏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.79,0:10:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 关系到大家的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.27,0:11:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失…失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.67,0:11:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失…失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.58,0:11:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.58,0:11:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入舰桥时 无须寒暄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.38,0:11:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃… 是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.79,0:11:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚利小姐比较较真
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.02,0:11:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不反感寒暄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.73,0:11:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 王
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.36,0:11:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有话大声说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.87,0:11:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 伊桑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.32,0:11:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵 先让我填饱肚子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.00,0:11:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这份是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.10,0:12:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.03,0:12:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.18,0:12:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长 启航准备完成
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.37,0:12:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.33,0:12:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.06,0:12:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就启航
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.50,0:12:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启航 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.94,0:12:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退开 吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.41,0:12:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里了结你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.59,0:12:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法·泽奥斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.28,0:13:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.57,0:13:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维甘没有人性
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.24,0:13:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀人不眨眼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.88,0:13:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.61,0:13:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是奥利巴诺兹？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.97,0:13:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神号
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.05,0:13:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是驾驶高达的菲利特·明日野
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.65,0:13:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面 我叫纳图尔·艾娜斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.97,0:13:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你该明白 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.89,0:13:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是反击的关键
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 我们？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.20,0:13:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你该明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.88,0:13:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是反击的关键
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.02,0:14:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是…反击的关键？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.18,0:14:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快下命令
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.63,0:14:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿比斯队等你的指示呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.93,0:14:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.51,0:14:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会打仗的人 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.58,0:14:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长这样 前途堪忧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.88,0:14:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两台机体完成维护可以出击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.66,0:14:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.53,0:14:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德雷克 奥布莱特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.75,0:14:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以出击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.89,0:14:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 灭了他们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.60,0:14:30.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.55,0:14:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,助天神号扭转战局
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.88,0:14:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿比斯队 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.03,0:14:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神号 准备好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.78,0:14:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,击落敌人母舰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,击落母舰是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.67,0:14:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要发射光子爆破炮吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.35,0:14:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.62,0:14:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那东西破坏力太强
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.76,0:14:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大气层内不能使用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.75,0:14:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投射高达的新武器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.45,0:15:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新…武器？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.48,0:15:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你！没有启动AGE系统吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.05,0:15:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.59,0:15:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AGE系统的话已经启动了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.66,0:15:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是洛蒂·麦德纳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.59,0:15:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日野老司令
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出动天神号是为了AGE系统吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.46,0:15:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.97,0:15:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才一直在试
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.79,0:15:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有出错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.37,0:15:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制造新武器的战斗数据不足
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.62,0:15:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 动手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.72,0:15:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把设计系统的报警等级降至30以下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.84,0:15:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强行完成构筑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.33,0:15:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 不知会造出什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.39,0:15:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了 快照办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.76,0:15:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有新武器能扭转乾坤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.70,0:15:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有新武器 就能击落母舰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.66,0:15:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后还得看你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.90,0:15:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坚持到武器完成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.57,0:15:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.26,0:15:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 继续
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.16,0:15:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达缓口气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.54,0:16:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.35,0:16:04.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用客气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.88,0:16:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从现在起高达归我指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.49,0:16:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡说什么 我们独立行动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.85,0:16:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是菲利特·明日野
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.85,0:16:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但您已经退伍了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.12,0:16:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 现在需要互相协助
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.02,0:16:23.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碍事的话 两台一起干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.88,0:16:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去迂回背面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.36,0:16:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.80,0:16:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.45,0:16:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新兵器的构筑还没完成吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.62,0:16:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.38,0:17:27.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.29,0:17:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附件大幅提高了西格玛希斯步枪的输出功率
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.70,0:17:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子相当危险
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.58,0:17:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.82,0:17:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.04,0:17:45.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留意装填时间比较长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.43,0:17:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武器代号 魔道加农
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.09,0:17:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即是小型光子环阵列
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.87,0:18:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用步枪光束射出附件积聚的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.91,0:18:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能量充填
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.33,0:18:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.04,0:18:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.58,0:18:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.26,0:18:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各机 集火高达
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.75,0:18:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护高达
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.64,0:18:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全体防御
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.82,0:18:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.60,0:18:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达 还没好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.69,0:18:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.70,0:18:37.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差一点了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.70,0:18:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.31,0:18:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.52,0:18:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.58,0:18:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉欧 你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.80,0:18:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然要打…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.60,0:19:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.50,0:19:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好 吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.17,0:19:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.69,0:20:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AGE系统
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.25,0:20:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,造出这么个怪物兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.77,0:20:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 轻易动用不了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.87,0:20:17.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日野老司令
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.17,0:20:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是队长 舍利奇·阿比斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.82,0:20:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.76,0:20:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.01,0:20:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.68,0:20:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.15,0:20:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么离开我们的队列
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.11,0:20:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我们的防御没有信心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.48,0:20:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱惜生命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.70,0:20:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.39,0:20:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.40,0:20:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.11,0:20:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是舰长纳图尔·艾娜斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.50,0:21:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本舰即将前往新设总司令部
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.89,0:21:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失落·楼兰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.31,0:21:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.44,0:21:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.79,0:21:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法发挥舰船实力的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.76,0:21:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不配当舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.97,0:21:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记住
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.62,0:21:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长担负着全船人的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.13,0:21:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.98,0:21:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.86,0:21:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.10,0:21:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你信得过高达吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.94,0:21:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.41,0:21:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达回应了我的操纵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.83,0:21:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.06,0:21:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.94,0:21:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊泽尔坎特是维甘的首领吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.07,0:22:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 他是邪恶的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.05,0:22:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想毁灭人类的魔王
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.31,0:22:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须被消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.30,0:22:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要消灭他们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.53,0:22:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消灭那些伤天害理的维甘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.23,0:22:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这台
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.93,0:22:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷的高达
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------NEXT------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.97,0:24:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙漠的亡灵逼近舰船
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.39,0:24:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踏上战斗之路的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.08,0:24:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的觉悟受到挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.63,0:24:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 机动战士高达AGE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.20,0:24:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战栗 沙漠的亡灵
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.88,0:24:12.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三个人的命运成就历史
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TVCM------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.77,0:24:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神号已经成为老旧舰船
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.14,0:24:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是经过多次改修
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.06,0:24:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍然拥有不输第一线战舰的性能
